item.description:
We had such a nice time here in March that I decided to do this one again. We'll walk along the trails and beach then head over to the Pavilion for a Picnic. Please bring something to share for the Picnic. You can post a comment below as to what you are bringing.

Carpooling from Manchester will be at the Youngsville Baseball field and parking lot off Candia Road at 12:00 High Noon.
item.how_to_find_us: Plunk will be the beagle screaming "Heyyyyy Over Here !!! "
